<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,1663,1689]" pageId="14" pageNumber="201">Etymology</emphasis>
. It gives us a great pleasure to dedicate this new species to Dr. Thomas J. Henry for his many outstanding contributions to the study of the 
<taxonomicName box="[617,753,1699,1725]" class="Insecta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Heteroptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="201" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Heteroptera</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
